            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "No proper teaching staff( it kept on changing every month) . There were only 7 kids in her class and still not enough space in the classroom. The management is only interested in money but lack providing even basic facilities to the kids. I would say WORST school of haryana and dlf phase 1. They will show they have fancy teaching plan but everything is only on paper. The teachers could not teach well and then keep on blaming the kids. The good reviews by school staff only... Principal forced them to give good reviews.. No one wants to review good.. Principal is always in attitude..  She never give respect to staffs and students if any student came in her cabin she always say to staff and students get lost to my cabin don't ever come here.. She never listen to students... She always do what she wants to do... TRUST ME THIS IS THE WORST SCHOOL EVER...",
